{"tid":539445,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇基因改造人?","createTime":"2018-01-24T14:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T18:35:04.000Z","uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9780acc5a562a5b7ca34ced33adc02b086edf234","tid":539445,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"而家動物同植物都可以基因改造，可以除去自身嘅缺點，同時可以保留或者加入更多嘅優勢<br />\n咁如果係人類會點? 會唔會整到一個極聰明嘅人? 一個有超強抵抗力嘅人? 又或者係一個無咁易老化嘅人? <br />\n咁依個世界會唔會多咗好多類似牛頓，愛因斯坦嘅人?<br />\n高達都有新人類，雖然話有道德問題，但係我覺得依個世界實有國家秘密進行緊基因改造人，只係無公布出黎，因為一公布出黎實會畀人反對而終止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0223a7d4e66341fdf74fd156353713b8762669","tid":539445,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"軍事用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3650abcc1e9fe138a34a8dc90e58f1a3709f8b16","tid":539445,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d0223a7d4e66341fdf74fd156353713b8762669","tid":539445,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"軍事用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"可能有複製人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f11811f7f560e38cb4deae6373453ee7029984","tid":539445,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"整個終極毒撚出嚟等你班21世紀毒撚有返啲自信"},{"pid":"3481dd40d25b61aca08f997a63e7641b66b0543b","tid":539445,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"講出黎你可能唔信，但我就係其中一個<br />\n其實唔止我一個，一陣叫其他手足黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61846578f9b4fb086767004310f77858f61793","tid":539445,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3481dd40d25b61aca08f997a63e7641b66b0543b","tid":539445,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"講出黎你可能唔信，但我就係其中一個<br />\n其實唔止我一個，一陣叫其他手足黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好咁 一陣畀人的去照肺就唔好啦<br />\n快啲貼Bam 圖自爆左佢算"},{"pid":"3e147acc18607dc807af0ab9bd542902ffba6f6c","tid":539445,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講出黎你可能唔信，但我就係其中一個<br />\n其實唔止我一個，一陣叫其他手足黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>巴打唔好咁 一陣畀人的去照肺就唔好啦<br />\n快啲貼Bam 圖自爆左佢算</blockquote><br />\n興奮過頭唔為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次野未未床單煮煮末了吃料做想刷汗杉木南澳汽水噢噢"},{"pid":"54bb3515f85fd4765563371d2d2d5b3f565d639f","tid":539445,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"你要明白，基因唔代表一切<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/chromosomes/features/2012/blogging_the_human_genome_/blogging_the_human_genome_was_the_human_genome_project_a_failure_.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slate.com%2Farticles%2Fhealth_and_science%2Fchromosomes%2Ffeatures%2F2012%2Fblogging_the_human_genome_%2Fblogging_the_human_genome_was_the_human_genome_project_a_failure_.html&d=d7HHhTYFsV4hwRhSgS4PEePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=97dddeea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/chromosomes/features/2012/blogging_the_human_genome_/blogging_the_human_genome_was_the_human_genome_project_a_failure_.html</a><br />\n<br />\n就算DNA話你有問題，你都可能未必有事。相對地，你整到話你啲基因係完美都好，你都可以變成碌廢柴。"},{"pid":"738839e0ab2e7a19d466eb7061f3eb460f8ab839","tid":539445,"uid":116289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/225337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg